{
  "texts": [
    "Specific word and bit lines were biased to V op and grounded to access the selected cell in the CA, and the rest of the lines were biased to the inhibiting voltages according to the bias scheme.",
    "In this study, 1/3 V op and 2/3 V op were applied as inhibiting voltages.",
    "Data preprocessing.",
    "The original 28 × 28 pixel MNIST images were subjected to a center-cropping process to reduce their size to 24 × 24 pixels.",
    "This cropping technique helped highlight the central regions of interest."
  ]
}